hope today that ARATS and SEF will expand exchanges in order to
improve mutual understanding between people on both sides of the
Straits.
</P>
<P>
Shi arrived in Beijing yesterday to join ARATS officials in
making arrangements for the forthcoming Koo visit.
</P>
<P>
