the United Nations," the Afghan Islamic Press quoted Taliban
spokesman Abdul Hae Mutmaen as saying.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, hundreds of religious scholars were meeting in the
Afghan capital of Kabul to advise the Taliban on how to handle the
Iranian threat, the radio report said.
</P>
<P>
The religious scholars denounced Iran's deployment of 200,000
troops along Afghanistan's western border and said it showed
Iran's intention to invade. 
