and Equatorial Guinea are Democratic Congo's neighbors in central
Africa along with Sudan, Uganda, Rwanda and Burundi.
</P>
<P>
Chad had already expressed support for Kabila, saying it might
send troops to join Zimbabwe, Namibia and Angola in helping
Kabila fight the rebellion. 
