The Magistrate's Court earlier on Tuesday ordered the
unconditional release of Anwar's another private secretary,
Mohamed Azmin Ali.
</P>
<P>
Ahmad was ordered to be remanded on September 15 for five days
upon his detention the day earlier under the Criminal Procedure
Code in connection with police investigations into the book "50
Dalil Mengapa Anwar Tidak Boleh Jadi PM" (50 reasons why Anwar
cannot become PM).
</P>
<P>
