<HEADLINE> Vegetable "King" in China's Desert (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Now, Gao's vegetables are found not only in the markets of
Yulin, but are also being sold to other provinces. In July, Gao
signed a contract with an Israeli demonstration farm based in
Beijing to sell 85,000 kg of vegetables to Beijing in October.
</P>
<P>
Gao said his vegetables sell well, except in the summer off
season.
</P>
